Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.20,0:03:41.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.53,0:03:43.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.53,0:03:44.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,安全上垒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.70,0:03:48.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,迟到的岚山  早班会的时候就给我站在走廊上反省吧
